- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on swarm-robotic systems and proposes metrics for evaluating their performance. 
- cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) is also likely as the paper deals with the behavior of a large number of robots working together as a swarm. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper discusses the design process of a swarm-robotic system. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes algorithms for swarm-robotic systems. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper proposes metrics for evaluating the performance of different algorithms.
